name: Embroidered Snow Baubles
description:
Embroidered fabric hanging tree baubles, based on original lino-print.
Available in Blue, Pink or Peach.
Dimensions: 100mm x 80mm with 180mm hang.

name: Richard III
description:
Meet Richard.  He's very sensitive about his hunchback.  Try not to mention it.
Signed hand-cut and hand printed lino using water-based inks and gold leaf.  Based on original drawings. 

Dimensions: (A4) 295 x 210 mm (Unframed)

name: George
description:
Meet George.  He lacks Stanley's finesse, but is all the more loveable for it.
Signed hand-cut and hand printed lino using water-based inks and gold leaf.  Based on original drawings. 

Dimensions: (A4) 295 x 210 mm (Unframed)

name: Stanley
description:
Meet Stanley.  He's a grumpy, if regal, crow.  It's only because he knows he was here first. 
Signed hand-cut and hand printed lino using water-based inks and gold leaf.  Based on original drawings. 

Dimensions: (A4) 295 x 210 mm (Unframed)

name: Canadian Rough Boys
description:
Say 'Hi' to the Canadian Rough Boys as they head South.
Set of three, signed hand-cut and hand printed lino using water-based inks.  Based on original drawings. 

Individual Dimensions: 150 x 100 mm (Unframed)

name: Blue Tile Print Smelly Nelly
description:
The Smelly Nelly is a hand-made, shaped, lavender-scented hanging bag.

Each one uses vintage, upcycled or printed fabrics, and has it's own 'smelly' label.  A perfect tongue-in-cheek gift.

Filled with British lavender buds and hypo-allergenic stuffing, the fragrance should last approx two years, just give a good squeeze to refresh.

Dimensions: 150 x 130mm not including ribbon

Not suitable for children under 3yrs to play with due to small parts.
